## 📋 COMPONENT CHECKLIST

Before creating a new component:

```markdown
Design:
☐ Can I compose from existing atoms?
☐ Is this a reusable pattern or one-off?
☐ Does it follow atomic hierarchy?

Accessibility:
☐ Keyboard navigation works
☐ ARIA labels present
☐ Focus management handled
☐ Screen reader tested
☐ Color contrast OK

Performance:
☐ Animations use GPU
☐ prefers-reduced-motion respected
☐ No unnecessary re-renders

Documentation:
☐ Props documented
☐ Variants shown
☐ Accessibility notes
☐ Usage examples
```

---

## 🎯 QUICK REFERENCE

```
Atomic Design:
├─ Atoms → Simple, no state, composable
├─ Molecules → 2-3 atoms combined
├─ Organisms → Complex components
├─ Templates → Page layouts
└─ Pages → Specific instances

Accessibility:
├─ Keyboard navigation (Tab, Enter, Escape)
├─ ARIA labels on interactive elements
├─ Focus indicators visible
├─ WCAG AA contrast (4.5:1)
└─ Screen reader announcements

Animations:
├─ Purpose over decoration
├─ prefers-reduced-motion check
├─ GPU only (transform/opacity)
└─ 200-400ms for UI

Anti-Patterns:
├─ Don't copy trends blindly
├─ Don't over-animate
├─ Don't ignore a11y
└─ Don't skip design tokens
```

---

## ⚠️ Anti-Patterns

| ❌ NEVER | ✅ ALWAYS | Why |
|---------|-----------|-----|
| Low contrast text | WCAG AA contrast minimum (4.5:1) | Accessibility |
| Tiny touch targets (< 44px) | Minimum 44x44px targets | Mobile usability |
| Color-only indicators | Icons + colors | Color blindness accessibility |
| Auto-playing media | User-controlled media | Accessibility, UX |
| Unclear error messages | Specific, actionable errors | User guidance |
| Infinite scroll without pagination | Load more button | Performance, control |
| Not keyboard navigable | Full keyboard support | Accessibility |

---

## 🔧 Troubleshooting

| Problem | Cause | Solution |
|---------|-------|----------|
| **"Poor accessibility score"** | Missing ARIA labels, low contrast | Use Lighthouse, add ARIA, increase contrast |
| **"Users can't find features"** | Poor information architecture | User testing, card sorting |
| **"High drop-off rate"** | Confusing navigation, long forms | Simplify flow, progress indicators |
| **"Mobile complaints"** | Not responsive, small touch targets | Test on real devices |
| **"Slow perceived performance"** | No loading feedback | Add skeletons, spinners, progress bars |

